Hardware
Waterproof and UV-resistant adhesive labels
Environmental & Agriculture Sensors – Help ensure 
environmental durability standards for label adhesion 
and material longevity in field conditions

Optional laminated or tamper-proof formats
Zigbee Accessories – Offer supporting tamper-evidence 
components and smart tagging integration compatible with QR/barcode formats

Printed QR codes and 1D/2D barcodes (EAN-13, Code 128, Data Matrix, etc.)
Optical & Imaging Sensors – Facilitate high-precision 
reading and validation of printed codes for livestock identification.

Handheld or mobile barcode/QR code scanners
Industrial Tablet PCs – Serve as portable data terminals 
for scanning and managing animal records through code-based ID systems.
